Package: gtsf
Type: Package
Title: General Transit Simple Features
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: as.person(c(
    "Tom Buckley <buckley.tom@gmail.com> [aut,cre]",
    "Danton Noriega-Goodwin <danton.noriega@gmail.com> [aut]",
    "Michael Sumner [aut]"
  ))
Description: Functions to get simple features from general transit feed data. For example, make a simple features data frame of the route lines, or route stops, that vehicles traverse as part of their schedule.   
